did.unittitle: United Board for Christian Higher Education in Asia Records - Addendum D
did.abstract: This record group represents a continuation of the official archives of the United Board for Christian Higher Education in Asia, supplementing and overlapping the papers in record groups 11, 11A, 11B, and 11C. It provides information about the institutions and projects to which the United Board has lent its support. The United Board for Chrisian Higher Education in Asia supports educational work in China, Hong Kong, India, Indonesia, Japan, Korea, Pakistan, The Philippines, Republic of China (Taiwan).

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: United Board for Christian Higher Education in Asia Records - Addendum D (RG 11D), Special Collections, Yale Divinity School Library.

bioghist.head: Biographical / Historical
bioghist.p: Information about the work of the United Board for Christian Higher Education during the period represented by these archives is contained in Paul Lauby's book Sailing on Winds of Change: Two Decades in the Life of the United Board for Christian Higher Education in Asia, 1969-1990 .

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The files have been maintained as sent by the United Board.
